title: Biden Inauguration, Rep. Carolyn Maloney
itunes:title: Biden Inauguration, Rep. Carolyn Maloney
description:
Guests: Bloomberg politics contributors Jeanne Sheehan Zaino, Iona College Professor and Rick Davis, Partner at Stone Court Capital, former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, and Rep. Carolyn Maloney, a Democrat representing New York's 12th congressional district.
